🔹 Project Aim

The aim of this project is to develop a “Productivity Mobile Application” using Kodular (MIT App Inventor platform).

This application helps users improve daily productivity by providing multiple useful features in a single app, such as:

To-Do List (task management)
Reminder system
Expense Tracker
Study Timer
Weather updates
Daily Tips
Calculator
Schedule planner
About section

The app is designed with a simple, user-friendly interface that allows easy navigation between different features.

🔹 Application Overview

The application consists of multiple screens, each handling a specific functionality.
Users can navigate between screens using buttons from the main menu.

