🔸 Screen 2: To-Do List Screen
Algorithm:

Initialize:

global tasks ← empty list
User enters task in TextBox.
When Add Task button is clicked:
Check if TextBox is empty:
If empty → do nothing or show message
Else:
Add TextBox.Text to global tasks list
Update ListView elements with global tasks
Clear TextBox
Display all tasks in ListView.
🔸 Screen 3: Reminder Screen
Algorithm:
User inputs reminder text and time.
When reminder is set:
Store reminder details
Display confirmation message
(Optional) Trigger notification or alert.
🔸 Screen 4: Expense Tracker Screen
Algorithm:
User enters expense amount and description.
When Add button clicked:
Store expense in list
Update total expense
Display list of expenses.
🔸 Screen 5: Study Timer Screen
Algorithm:
User selects study time.
When Start button clicked:
Start timer countdown
When time finishes:
Show alert/message "Time Up"
🔸 Screen 6: Weather Screen
Algorithm:
Fetch weather data (API or static display)
Display:
Temperature
Weather condition
Update periodically.
🔸 Screen 7: Daily Tips Screen
Algorithm:

Generate random tip using:

random integer from 1 to 3
If:
1 → "Drink Water 💧"
2 → "Take a Break 🧠"
3 → "Go for a Walk 🚶"
Display tip in Label.
🔸 Screen 8: Calculator Screen
Algorithm:

User inputs two numbers.

Buttons perform operations:

Addition:

result = num1 + num2

Subtraction:

result = num1 - num2

Multiplication:

result = num1 × num2
Division:
If num2 = 0:
→ show "Cannot divide by 0"

Else:

result = num1 / num2

Display result in Label.

